value.string: Super Luxury Off The Grid!!! Custom 2,264 sqft home on 5 manicured North Shore acres! This estate is in perfect condition. Meticulous maintenance standards. Electric power is generated on property; full communications center gourmet chef's kitchen. Private owners suite, outstanding inventory and landscaping. So near yet so far removed. Prime horse country! Experience fine living.

A single story residence with sunset views and located close to parks, beaches and Lahaina Town. This 4 bed 2 bath cinder block home has a 2 bed 2 bath detached Ohana with rental income potential or for family and guest while visiting on island. Upgrades include Star Energy Saver windows and doors, hard wood Pergo flooring, new carpet in bedrooms, Marble tile flooring and new cabinets in kitchen and counter tops in kitchen and baths, composite shingle 50 year roof and paint. New solar water heater and an attic exhaust fan has been installed to cool entire house down. Ceiling fans throughout with termite resistant Redwood interior walls. Mango and Papaya trees on property with the most delicious fruits to enjoy. Sold unfurnished but all appliances are included in sale. New septic tank installed for Ohana. Buyer is to do own due diligence as some improvements to Ohana are not to county code.
